snippet.title: Monkey Magic C64 Tape Loader
snippet.description:
Monkey Magic for C64 by Solar Software, loaded from tape

This one I got on an OziSoft compilation of 10 games (a few solar softwar egames, a few gremlin games, and a few originals - monty mole, robin to the rescue, and potty pidgeon were highlights).  I'm 100% sure this is completly unlicensed from the original show, and the mary poppins music is a nice touch.

It's objectivly bad, but yet I enjoy it anyhow.  You probably shouldn't play it, but I never regret loading it.  I hear the Commodore 16 version is actually superior to this, mind you.
